{"tid":2493982,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"消防已尋回疑行山失蹤女子石樂蕎　正移動到安全位置","createTime":"2021-04-18T10:15:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-18T10:21:58.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"949232e509e873194f8d79e880c03044b16b1b4f","tid":2493982,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T10:15:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1586431-20210418.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1586431-20210418.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=suC3bgMk4yzoLj7oQdk4RAwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=64706c5e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1586431-20210418.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=7f5b4eff\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1586431-20210418.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n當局表示，已找到24歲懷疑行山失蹤的女子石樂蕎，正移動到安全地方。<br />\n<br />\n消防和警方昨晚起派出約120人在飛鵝山搜索和調查。<br />\n<br />\n消防昨晚在鵝肚棧道附近找到一對事主的行山鞋，強調會以一切可行資源繼續搜索。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，事主電話訊號最後出現位置的發射站在新蒲崗一間工業大廈，時間是昨日上午。"},{"pid":"4940a5452987e45754838461d2d276db74d53134","tid":2493982,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T10:17:16.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人要冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00aeb02c2368f8736c78810fca774a9edd640073","tid":2493982,"uid":353208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T10:18:07.000Z","msg":"人無事 🙏🙏🙏"},{"pid":"f9fe786fea45f2f9289075396cca67acdf6e41d1","tid":2493982,"uid":306337,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T10:18:38.000Z","msg":"竟然仲在生"},{"pid":"a991d878aec86c37a4721ef7f5fa982d61b86fb8","tid":2493982,"uid":92125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T10:21:58.000Z","msg":"移動？"}]}